Author: Jake
Content: I might not have a large enough following to make this work yet but wouldn't it be awesome if I could write a blog post request for a startup, solicit interest in actually building it, raise capital to pay for the work, and have the product come to life, all through Twitter?! Quote Tweet Jake @blogofjake  · Jan 6 Yesterday I tweeted an idea for a podcast player organized by guest rather than host/show.   Today someone followed up and let me know how they'd build the mvp and how long it would take to do.  Long shot, would anyone be down to fund it ~$2K for the mvp?  https://blogofjake.com/2021/01/04/request-for-startup-a-new-kind-of-podcast-platform/…
